---
// "The Proof" amber CTA slab - ink on spot colour, glows in dark mode
---
<section id="contact" class="bg-spot-surface py-20 md:py-24 px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
    <p class="label-mono text-spot-ink/60 mb-6">Enquiries &mdash; replies within a few hours</p>
    <h2 class="font-display text-spot-ink text-4xl md:text-5xl lg:text-6xl leading-[1] tracking-[-0.03em] max-w-[14ch] mb-7" style="font-weight: 780;">
      Ready when you are.
    </h2>
    <p class="text-spot-ink/75 text-lg max-w-xl mb-9 leading-relaxed">
      Tell us what you need and we'll come back with a fixed quote. No long forms, no commitment.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-6">
      <a
        href="https://wa.me/27814623628?text=Hi%2C%20I%27d%20like%20to%20discuss%20a%20project%20with%20Lumina7"
        target="_blank"
        rel="noopener noreferrer"
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-7 py-3.5 text-sm font-semibold text-[#F6F4EF] bg-[#16140F] rounded-full hover:-translate-y-px transition-transform duration-300 group focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-[#16140F] focus-visible:ring-offset-2 focus-visible:ring-offset-spot"
        data-event="whatsapp_click"
        data-event-source="cta_slab"
      >
        <span>WhatsApp us</span>
        <span class="group-hover:translate-x-0.5 transition-transform duration-300" aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span>
      </a>
      <a
        href="/contact"
        class="text-sm font-medium text-spot-ink/75 hover:text-spot-ink underline underline-offset-4 transition-colors duration-300 focus-visible:outline-none focus-visible:ring-2 focus-visible:ring-[#16140F] rounded-[4px]"
        data-event="contact_form_link_click"
        data-event-source="cta_slab"
      >
        or send us a message
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
